## Verification Plan

### Automated/Scripted Tests
We will verify endpoints using a local command line script executing requests using a standard client tool.

### Manual Verification
1. Open the React frontend locally.
2. Go to `/register` and create a test account.
3. Verify redirection to the dashboard, storage of JWT token in localStorage, and appearance of the Navbar displaying the user's name.
4. Log out, verify redirect to `/login`, and attempt to access protected `/dashboard` path directly to confirm route locks.
5. Log back in to verify the login flow.
